      "title": "Ukrainian President expels foreign ambassadors",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign news services report that Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky has decided to expel several foreign ambassadors.",
        "Ukrainian President Zelensky has expelled German, Indian, Czech, Norwegian and Hungarian ambassadors to Ukraine.",
        "Why President Zelenskiy expelled these ambassadors has not yet been revealed."
